  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "</b> </i>] [<i>Provides that real estate teams are not required to change terms used in the team name until July 1, 2027.</i>] <b>Delays until July 1, 2027, the requirement that a real estate team change the terms used in the team name.</b> Declares an emergency, effective on passage."
